            <summary>Tirée de differentz Autheurs latins, françois, Italiens et Espagnolz. Illustrated with a pen-drawn horoscopic figure (p.141) and a circular figure (p. 234). In the lower margin of the 'Table des chapitres' and of the 'Preface', is the name 'Ballisdens' in gold ink, by a contemporary hand. This is probably an autograph signature of Jean Balesdens [ -1675], French jurist and Author.</summary>
